name: Improvisation of SAMO (2021 - GIF)
description:
Improvisation of SAMO. Just like what he did in the past. His painting like Jazz music. Pretty much wild and full of improvisation. 

Inspired with my figure drawing about a legendary painter, Jean Michael basquiat. I decided make it on image digital collaged animation. Combine with my abstract painting and my figure drawing of Basquiat. 

Come in GIF Image. Digital asset of NFT. 1250 x 1718 pixel.
